Go to this link and select your O/S and download


https://www.getpostman.com/apps



after downloading it is a  tar file like this-
Postman-linux-x64-6.0.10.tar.gz

extract the folder , open this and run the executing file name as postman 


//////////////////////////////////////////  OR //////////////////////////////////////////

Open your terminal by pressing Ctrl+Alt+T and install the Postman snap package, by typing:

sudo snap install postman




